lettings.views module¶

lettings.views.index(request)¶

Renders lettings list page with all Letting objects from the database. Fetches Lettings, packs them into context, and returns rendered template.

Parameters:

request (object) – http request object.

Returns:

http response with context

Return type:

tuple[request, html, dict[list[dict]]

lettings.views.letting(request, letting_id)¶

Renders a detailed page for a single Letting object identified by letting_id. Fetches the Letting, creates context with details, and renders the template.

Parameters:

  • request (object) – http request object.

  • letting_id (int) – letting id.

Returns:

http response with context

Return type:

tuple[request, html, dict[str, dict]
